@startuml
title UC04 Client application calls the gateway API

participant "Client application" as Client
participant "Enki Gate API" as API
database "Firestore" as Firestore
collections "Cloud KMS" as KMS
participant "Upstream provider" as Provider
participant "Cloud Logging" as Logging

Client -> API: Call the OpenAI-compatible API\nwith a gateway token
API -> Firestore: Validate the token issuance and current access state
Firestore --> API: actor / credential owner / credential data
API -> KMS: Request key operations needed for decryption
KMS --> API: Return decryption material
API -> Provider: Forward the request with the provider API key
Provider --> API: Response and usage metadata
API -> Logging: Record request and usage events
API --> Client: Return the OpenAI-compatible response
@enduml
